transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Hello?
Customer: Haan ji sir.
Executive: Haan.
Customer: Abhi hoga system aapke pass?
Customer: Phone se bolo aap phone se hoga usme nahi hota hai.
Executive: Sir main batati hu aapko main batati hu kaise hoga usme connect jaise ki aap laptop on karoge na aap chrome me jaake
Executive: WhatsApp web search karna.
Executive: Thik hai.
Executive: WhatsApp web jab aap search karoge na us pe aap click karna ek scanner bana hua aayega.
Executive: To jab aap whatsapp open karoge na waha pe ek aata hai na scan bana hua whatsapp ke andar us pe click karna wo scanner jo hai waha pe scan karna to aapka jo hai whatsapp waha pe login ho jayega.
Customer: Are waha pe login to ho gaya hai lekin waha pe open nahi ho raha.
Executive: Link.
Customer: Link open nahi ho raha aapki.
Executive: Kya aa raha hai link mein?
Customer: Verify ka aa raha hai verify kar raha hu fir bhi usme open ho nahi raha hai.
Executive: Verify kar rahe hai to open ho nahi raha hai. Ek baar mujhe screenshot leke bhej doge sir?
Customer: Phone se karo then waha pe maine sab kuch kar rakha hai lekin waha pe nahi hota phone se karo.
Executive: Phone pe sir main aapko kar lungi usme mujhe koi issue nahi aayega but ya to aap mujhe koi another number bata do sir jisse ki main aapse baat kar paun kyuki us pe na audio video call pe fir voice clear nahi aa pati hai na na aapki mere ko aayegi na meri aapko ja payegi.
Executive: To fir samajh mein aayega nahi sir.
Customer: mujhe kisi aur ka number bata dijiye.
Customer: Dusra mera number hai us pe whatsapp call karna padega aapko.
Executive: WhatsApp call jo ek minute jo aapka ye wala number hai 9765 part hai 619 hai end mein.
Customer: Haan haan wo whatsapp number hai whatsapp karna padega wo.
Executive: To aap mujhe sir ye number na aap mere ko whatsapp pe share kar do fir main aapko connect kar leti hu audio call ke through.
Customer: Thik hai thik hai.
Executive: Thik hai sir okay.
Customer: .

- Customer unable to open link on WhatsApp web.

- Voice not clear on audio/video call.

- Executive explained how to connect WhatsApp web.

- Customer to share alternate number on WhatsApp.

- Executive will connect via audio call.
